<h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,42px);line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:800">Top Marketplaces in Ukraine 2026: A Complete Guide for International Brands</h1>
<p style="color:#888;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px">Updated: April 2026 &middot; Reading time: 12 min</p>

<img src="/images/blog/top-marketplaces-ukraine-hero.webp" alt="Top marketplaces in Ukraine 2026 — guide for international sellers" style="width:100%;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:32px" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">

<p>Ukraine&rsquo;s e-commerce market exceeded $8 billion (200+ billion UAH) in 2025 and continues growing 20-25% annually. For international brands looking to enter this market, local marketplaces offer the fastest path to Ukrainian consumers &mdash; without building your own website or local marketing team.</p>

<div style="background:#e63329;color:#fff;padding:20px 24px;border-radius:12px;margin:24px 0">
<strong style="font-size:18px">No Ukrainian entity needed.</strong>
<p style="margin:8px 0 0;opacity:.9">MTP Group acts as your local logistics partner. We handle warehousing, fulfillment, shipping, returns, and payment collection. You focus on product and marketing. <a href="/en/" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:underline">Learn more &rarr;</a></p>
</div>

<div style="background:#000;color:#fff;padding:20px 24px;border-radius:12px;margin:24px 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;text-align:center">
