<div><span style="font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#e63329;display:block">50%</span><span style="font-size:12px;opacity:.6">cheaper than EU</span></div>
<div><span style="font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#e63329;display:block">10K+</span><span style="font-size:12px;opacity:.6">Nova Poshta locations</span></div>
