<h2 style="margin-top:40px">Why Sell on Ukrainian Marketplaces?</h2>
<p>Ukraine offers a unique combination: large consumer base (44 million people), high smartphone penetration, rapidly growing e-commerce, and significantly lower fulfillment costs compared to EU countries. A typical fulfillment operation in Ukraine costs roughly 50% less than equivalent services in Poland or Germany.</p>
<p>Ukrainian consumers are price-sensitive but brand-loyal. Once they find a quality product at a fair price, repeat purchases are common. Cash-on-delivery (COD) remains the dominant payment method (~60% of orders), which means your fulfillment partner must handle payment collection &mdash; something <a href="/en/" style="color:#e63329">MTP Group</a> does automatically through our &ldquo;Sheriff of Payments&rdquo; system.</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:40px">The Big 7: Ukrainian Marketplaces</h2>

<h3>1. Rozetka &mdash; Ukraine&rsquo;s Amazon</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-rozetka-homepage.webp" alt="Rozetka marketplace homepage" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>30+ million monthly visits. The dominant marketplace covering all categories. Commission 5-27% (average 15%). Platform fee 120 UAH/month (~$2.70). Supports both FBO (Rozetka warehouses) and FBS (seller ships) models.</p>
<p><strong>For international brands:</strong> Rozetka requires a Ukrainian legal entity (FOP or LLC) for registration. MTP Group can assist with the setup process. Once registered, product listing is done via API or XML feed &mdash; we handle the logistics side completely.</p>

<h3>2. Prom.ua &mdash; Lowest Commission</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-prom-homepage.webp" alt="Prom.ua marketplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>The second-largest marketplace. Commission from just 2.1% (Economy mode) to 4.2% (standard). Annual packages from 6,700 UAH (~$152) for 1,000 products. No FBO &mdash; seller handles logistics (or uses 3PL like MTP Group).</p>
<p><strong>For international brands:</strong> Prom creates a full storefront for your brand on their platform. Lower commission means higher margins &mdash; especially attractive for high-volume sellers. Integration via API available.</p>

<h3>3. Kasta &mdash; Fashion &amp; Lifestyle</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-kasta-homepage.webp" alt="Kasta fashion marketplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>Ukraine&rsquo;s #1 fashion marketplace. Commission 3-20% + 20 UAH/unit for delivery and returns. No monthly fee. Next-day payouts. High return rate in fashion (30-40%).</p>
<p><strong>For international brands:</strong> Excellent for fashion, accessories, and beauty brands entering Ukraine. The flash-sale model drives high volumes during seasonal peaks (Black Friday, New Year, March 8).</p>

<h3>4. Allo &mdash; Electronics</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-allo-homepage.webp" alt="Allo electronics marketplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>10+ million monthly visits. Specializes in electronics, smartphones, laptops. Commission 5-12%. Omnichannel advantage: buyers can order online and pick up at 300+ physical stores.</p>

<h3>5. Epicentr &mdash; Home &amp; Construction</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-epicentr-homepage.webp" alt="Epicentr marketplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>One of Ukraine&rsquo;s largest retailers. Commission 5-25% (CPS model &mdash; only for completed orders). First deposit 1,100 UAH (~$25). Strong in construction materials, furniture, garden, home goods.</p>

<h3>6. MAKEUP &mdash; Beauty &amp; Cosmetics</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-makeup-homepage.webp" alt="MAKEUP beauty marketplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>Premium beauty marketplace. Commission 10-20%. Only authentic products with certificates. FEFO (First Expired, First Out) control required. Highly engaged female audience 18-45.</p>
<p><strong>For beauty brands:</strong> MTP Group provides <a href="/en/fulfillment-for-marketplaces/" style="color:#e63329">FEFO-compliant storage</a> for cosmetics and supplements. Our client Elemis has worked with us for 7+ years without a single storage complaint.</p>

<h3>7. OLX &mdash; Free Start</h3>
<img src="/images/blog/marketplace-olx-homepage.webp" alt="OLX marketplace Ukraine" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #eee;margin-bottom:16px" loading="lazy">
<p>15+ million visitors. C2C format but works for business too. Free basic listings. OLX Delivery via Nova Poshta with buyer protection. Ideal for market testing with zero investment.</p>

