<h2 style="margin-top:48px">How to Enter Ukrainian Marketplaces (Without a Local Entity)</h2>

<div style="background:#fafafa;padding:24px;border-radius:12px;margin:20px 0">
<p style="font-size:15px;margin:0 0 16px">Most Ukrainian marketplaces require a local legal entity (FOP &mdash; sole proprietorship or LLC). But you don&rsquo;t need to set it up yourself. Here&rsquo;s how international brands work with MTP Group:</p>
<ol style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;line-height:2">
<li><strong>Contact MTP Group</strong> &mdash; free consultation, we assess your product fit for the Ukrainian market</li>
<li><strong>Ship inventory to our warehouse</strong> near Kyiv (Boryspil or Bilohorodka)</li>
<li><strong>We handle local entity setup</strong> &mdash; guide you through FOP registration or act as your local partner</li>
<li><strong>We list products on marketplaces</strong> via API integration (Rozetka, Prom, Kasta)</li>
<li><strong>Orders flow automatically</strong> into our WMS &rarr; picked in 30 sec &rarr; shipped via Nova Poshta</li>
<li><strong>We collect payments</strong> (including cash-on-delivery) and transfer to your account</li>
</ol>
</div>

