<details style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;padding:16px 0"><summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">Can MTP Group handle everything for us?<span style="color:#e63329;font-size:20px">+</span></summary><p style="margin-top:12px;color:#666">Yes. We integrate with Rozetka, Prom.ua, Kasta via API. Orders flow automatically into our WMS. We handle: receiving inventory, storage, picking (30 sec/order), packing, shipping via Nova Poshta (4 pickups/day), returns processing, COD payment collection, and Telegram reporting.</p></details>
